This paper is about developing a dialogue generation model that is more empathetic towards users' expressed emotions. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper focuses on improving the emotional intelligence of dialogue systems, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound and Dialogue) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
